node.text:
Villa Cullinan is the winner of European Property Awards and considered as the Best Residential Property 2019-2020.
​
The mansion has everything for an excepcional, unique and the most luxurious living: value, location, super generous plot, picturesque setting, jaw-dropping views, top-quality construction, cutting-edge equipment, functionality and elegance of interiors, plus that wow factor that makes it truly special.

Casual gathering spaces, floor-to-ceiling windows, panoramic glass doors, state-of-art designer kitchen with premium equipment, amazing covered and sunny outdoor areas, majestic mountain scenery; sea, Africa and Gibraltar views - it is all about this dream house.
By: @drumelia_real_estate
​#TheLuxuryScene

node.text:
Tag your squad 😎
​
​By: @comfortrental.ae
​#theluxuryscene #urus #lamborghini #lamborghiniurus #mercedesgwagon #gwagon #gclass

Check out the @JacobandCo Opera Godfather Musical Watch 🎶

This timepiece combines high-end watchmaking with the complexity of a mechanical instrument box, playing the theme music of The Godfather, an official partnership with Paramount Pictures. 

The watch’s music box utilizes a total of 36 teeth turning against two combs to play a melody of 120 notes of The Godfather theme music.

If you look closely, you can notice the 18k gold piano keys moving, making contact with the pins of the cylinder, which produces the iconic soundtrack.

By: @jacobandco
#theluxuryscene #jacobandco #thegodfather #godfather #18kgold
